resources.string:
This is a game that extends the classic "Greedy Snake". You have to control the snake to eat apples in an order such that the letters in the snake body make up a word of which the Chinese meaning is given.
 Just as the classic game, you have to avoid collision with the wall and the snake itself during the moving. We add a new feature of "regret": you can give up an apple already eaten by eating an "@". Eat the "$" when you are finished with a word.
 Move Instructions: 
 . use direction key(up, down, left, right) to move the snake;
 . press ENTER to start/pause/resume game;
 . use MENU for other functions;
